   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "218.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "221.520", 
   "id": "s000059", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wenn wir einmal zu unserem n\u00f6rdlichen Nachbarn D\u00e4nemark schauen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "221.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "222.400", 
   "id": "s000060", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dann sehen wir, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "222.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "227.040", 
   "id": "s000061", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass sich das \u00d6kosystem der Start-ups dort massiv verbessert hat."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "227.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "227.840", 
   "id": "s000062", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Meine Damen und Herren, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "227.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "229.520", 
   "id": "s000063", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "festzuhalten ist also, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "229.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "232.640", 
   "id": "s000064", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass wir in Deutschland mehr tun k\u00f6nnen und m\u00fcssen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "232.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "238.840", 
   "id": "s000065", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "um vielversprechenden Gr\u00fcndern und jungen Unternehmen im Wachstum finanziellen Spielraum zu erm\u00f6glichen; "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "238.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "245.240", 
   "id": "s000066", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "denn so sichern wir unsere Wirtschaftskraft und unsere Arbeitspl\u00e4tze in der globalen Welt und erwirtschaften wir das Geld, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "245.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "247.840", 
   "id": "s000067", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "das wir f\u00fcr unseren Sozialstaat ben\u00f6tigen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "247.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "249.680", 
   "id": "s000068", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es ist der Mittelstand von morgen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "249.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "251.560", 
   "id": "s000069", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "den es hier zu f\u00f6rdern gilt."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "251.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "252.360", 
   "id": "s000070", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Herzlichen Dank."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "252.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "256.600", 
   "id": "s000071", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Vielen Dank, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "256.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "258.800", 
   "id": "s000072", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Herr Kollege Mohrs.\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
